{"tid":512231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑遭gathering女子迷魂 中年漢失金鏈手錶","createTime":"2017-12-28T09:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T14:20:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a23b5a62e4bda45614a30206634719d2f72ed2e","tid":512231,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:15:51.000Z","msg":"【17:04更新】警方正追緝一名操普通話的中國籍女子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171228/large/1514437620_8ff8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171228%2Flarge%2F1514437620_8ff8.jpg&h=7964c99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名57歲姓李男子於今早11時許報案，指在上水新成路與一女子兜搭後，到附近房間短聚。惟該女子點煙後，他隨即暈倒，至醒來時身上1條5兩重約值5萬元的金鍊、一隻約值28,000元的勞力士手錶，及約5,000元現金被盜去，懷疑是對方所為。<br />\n<br />\n李並無受傷，其後警員到場調查，他乘坐警車陪同警員在附近兜截涉事女子蹤影，但無發現。警方經初步調查，把案件列盜竊，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝一名操普通話的中國籍女子，她年約30至40歲，肥身材，案發時身穿黑色外套及灰色裙。"},{"pid":"1564ff55ac3f482c43cc0527283f3c7d421c0b15","tid":512231,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c57eb1b531e966ea36bc7d3ac7a8138f3e72199","tid":512231,"uid":15406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"肥身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258d0fa0a03f7be80ad6ca43a80d39c55be0577b","tid":512231,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b295af0fada8c6732ca9affefd97a0db237d05f","tid":512231,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"饑不擇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e668da6d89d537ea33737515da46d583e1a378","tid":512231,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r